Part 1.5 a - Experiment with various parameters to improve performance of the base model¶

In [36]:
leaf_size1 = list(range(1,50))
n_neighbors1 = list(range(1,30))
p1=[1,2]
hyperparameters1 = dict(leaf_size=leaf_size1, n_neighbors=n_neighbors1, p=p1)
knn_1 = KNeighborsClassifier()
clf = GridSearchCV(knn_1, param_grid = hyperparameters1, cv=10)
